You are cordially invited to attend the first Inaugural “DNA Diamond Ball” this March in Atlanta, Georgia. We are looking forward to a night of fundraising, networking, sophistication and beauty, we will honor and award different “Diamonds” in our community.  These amazing gems in Ghana now have clean water and food, shelter and a school (The DNA Brand Academy) because of each of you who held hands with us to make a difference 👊🏽. Join us at the ball for the making of history, being in the DNA archives and being part of the biggest impact for this community in #ghana and upcoming projects in #barbados + #novascotia 

Learn more about the evening and purchase tickets at www.thednadiamondball.com (link in bio)

When: Sunday, March 12, 2023
Where: The Thompson Hotel Buckhead Atlanta
Formal attire and tickets required for entry.

2023 oh what a ride ! Full Transparency ❤️ this year started off with plenty of question marks. At the start of the new year 23.. I silently made myself promises and as the year quickly passed, I knew I owed myself to keep the promises that only I knew of and prayed over.  Although the year has been filled with highs and lows, I happy to say, the highs far outweigh the lows. God really did his thing ! And so did I !

This has been a life-changing  year filled with new experiences 🙏🏽 and opportunities.. I’m grateful for this journey. Thank you to everybody who contributed to an amazing 2023. I couldn’t have done it without YOU. Thank you to everyone that has supported me I’m grateful for your support and don’t take it for granted. Thank you to everybody for prayers and encouragement when I needed it most. 🙏🏽 I’m ready for 2024. Hopefully you’ll be alone for the ride. LESTS GO!
